#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:104
msgid ""
"After comparing the various features, consider how these businesses, with "
"various inventory management and logistics workflows, came to their decision."
msgstr ""
"Efter att ha jämfört de olika funktionerna, överväg hur dessa företag, med "
"olika lagerhantering och logistikarbetsflöden, kom till sitt beslut."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:108
msgid "Pallets of items using packaging"
msgstr "Pallar med artiklar som använder förpackning"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:110
msgid ""
"A warehouse receives shipments of soap organized on physical pallets, each "
"containing 96 bars. These pallets are used for internal transfers and are "
"also sold as standalone units. For logistical purposes, the pallet's weight "
"must be included in the total shipping weight for certain deliveries. "
"Additionally, the pallet requires a barcode to facilitate tracking, and the "
"number of individual bars of soap must be included in the stock count when "
"the pallet is received."
msgstr ""
"Ett lager tar emot leveranser av tvål organiserad på fysiska pallar, var och "
"en innehållande 96 tvålstycken. Dessa pallar används för interna "
"överföringar och säljs också som fristående enheter. För logistiska ändamål "
"måste pallens vikt inkluderas i den totala transportervikten för vissa "
"leveranser. Dessutom kräver pallen en streckkod för att underlätta spårning, "
"och antalet enskilda tvålstycken måste inkluderas i lagerantalet när pallen "
"tas emot."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:116
msgid ""
"After evaluating various options, *product packaging* was the most suitable "
"solution. Packaging enables assigning a barcode to a pallet, identifying it "
"as a \"pallet type\" containing 96 soap bars. This barcode streamlines "
"operations by automatically registering the grouped quantity. Key "
"distinctions include:"
msgstr ""
"Efter att ha utvärderat olika alternativ var *produktförpackning* den mest "
"lämpliga lösningen. Förpackning möjliggör tilldelning av en streckkod till "
"en pall, identifierar den som en \"palltyp\" som innehåller 96 tvålstycken. "
"Denna streckkod effektiviserar processer genom att automatiskt registrera "
"den grupperade kvantiteten. Viktiga skillnader inkluderar:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:121
msgid ""
"**Warehouse tracking limitations**: Odoo tracks only the total quantity, not "
"the number of packagings. For instance, if a pallet with 12 and 24 "
"quantities is received, Odoo records 36 quantities, not the pallet details."
msgstr ""
"**Begränsningar i lagerspårning**: Odoo spårar endast den totala "
"kvantiteten, inte antalet förpackningar. Till exempel, om en pall med 12 och "
"24 kvantiteter tas emot, registrerar Odoo 36 kvantiteter, inte palldetaljer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:124
msgid ""
"**Packaging barcodes are type-specific, not unique**: Barcodes represent "
"packaging types (e.g., \"pallet of 96 soap bars\") but do not uniquely "
"identify individual pallets, such as Pallet #1 or Pallet #2."
msgstr ""
"**Förpackningsstreckkoder är typspecifika, inte unika**: Streckkoder "
"representerar förpackningstyper (t.ex. \"pall med 96 tvålstycken\") men "
"identifierar inte unikt enskilda pallar, såsom Pall #1 eller Pall #2."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:129
msgid "Capture product information using barcode"
msgstr "Fånga produktinformation med streckkod"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:131
msgid ""
"An Odoo user expects the **Barcode** app to display the typical storage "
"location of a product by scanning a barcode for a container."
msgstr ""
"En Odoo-användare förväntar sig att **Streckkoder**-appen ska visa den "
"typiska förvaringsplatsen för en produkt genom att skanna en streckkod för "
"en container."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:134
msgid ""
"*Packages* was the most suitable. When the :ref:`appropriate setting is "
"enabled <inventory/warehouses_storage/enable-package>`, scanning a package "
"barcode displays its contents in the **Barcode** app."
msgstr ""
"*Emballage* var det mest lämpliga. När :ref:`lämplig inställning är "
"aktiverad <inventory/warehouses_storage/enable-package>`, visar skanning av "
"en emballagestreckkod dess innehåll i **Streckkoder**-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:138
msgid ""
"Packages represent physical containers, enabling detailed tracking of the "
"items they hold. Scanning a package provides visibility into its contents "
"and facilitates operations, like inventory moves."
msgstr ""
"Emballage representerar fysiska behållare som möjliggör detaljerad spårning "
"av de objekt de innehåller. Att skanna ett emballage ger synlighet i dess "
"innehåll och underlättar processer som lagertransporter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:145
msgid "Track different units of measure in storage"
msgstr "Spåra olika måttenheter i förvar"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:147
msgid "A fruit juice distributor tracks multiple |UoMs| for their operations:"
msgstr "En fruktjuicedistributör spårar flera |UoMs| för sina processer:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:149
msgid "Fruits are purchased in tons."
msgstr "Frukt köps in i ton."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:150
msgid "Juice is produced and stored in kilograms."
msgstr "Juice produceras och förvaras i kilogram."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:151
msgid "Small samples are stored in grams for recipe testing."
msgstr "Små prover förvaras i gram för recepttestning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:153
msgid ""
"*Unit of Measure* was most suitable. Odoo automatically converts tons to "
"kilograms during receipts. However, since Odoo tracks only one |UoM| per "
"product in the database, the company uses lot numbers to differentiate |"
"UoMs|:"
msgstr ""
"*Måttenhet* var mest lämplig. Odoo konverterar automatiskt ton till kilogram "
"vid inleveranser. Men eftersom Odoo endast spårar en |UoM| per produkt i "
"databasen använder företaget partinummer för att särskilja |UoMs|:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:157
msgid "LOT1: Grams (g)"
msgstr "LOT1: Gram (g)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:158
msgid "LOT2: Kilograms (kg)"
msgstr "LOT2: Kilogram (kg)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure.rst:160
msgid ""
"Manual inventory adjustments are required to convert between lots, such as "
"subtracting 1 kg from LOT2 to add 1,000 g to LOT1. While functional, this "
"workaround can be time-consuming and prone to errors."
msgstr ""
"Manuella lagerkorrigeringar är nödvändiga för att konvertera mellan partier, "
"till exempel att subtrahera 1 kg från LOT2 för att lägga till 1 000 g till "
"LOT1. Även om det är funktionellt kan denna lösning vara tidskrävande och "
"felbenägen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:3
msgid "Pack-in-pack"
msgstr "Emballage i emballage"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:5
msgid ""
"In more complex warehouse operations, it is sometimes necessary to handle "
"groups of containers (for example, grouping pallets together). These "
"containers may be physically combined or logically grouped at the database "
"level, allowing them to be treated as a single unit for certain stock "
"movements while still retaining visibility into their internal structure. "
"This makes it possible to move the entire group with a single scan, rather "
"than scanning each pallet individually."
msgstr ""
"I mer komplexa lagerprocesser är det ibland nödvändigt att hantera grupper "
"av behållare (till exempel att gruppera pallar tillsammans). Dessa behållare "
"kan vara fysiskt kombinerade eller logiskt grupperade på databasnivå, vilket "
"gör det möjligt att behandla dem som en enda enhet för vissa "
"lagertransporter samtidigt som synligheten i deras interna struktur "
"bibehålls. Detta gör det möjligt att flytta hela gruppen med en enda "
"skanning, i stället för att skanna varje pall individuellt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:14
msgid ""
"Before working with the pack-in-pack settings, "
"open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Enable "
"the :guilabel:`Packages` setting. Be sure to click :guilabel:`Save` before "
"exiting this page."
msgstr ""
"Innan du arbetar med inställningarna för emballage i emballage, "
"öppna :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`. "
"Aktivera inställningen :guilabel:`Emballage`. Glöm inte att klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Spara` innan du lämnar denna sida."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:None
msgid "Enable Packages in the Inventory configuration settings."
msgstr "Aktivera Emballage i konfigurationsinställningarna för Lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:22
msgid "Set package type"
msgstr "Ställ in emballagetyp"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:24
msgid ""
"The *Set Package Type* setting must be enabled for all operations that "
"require pack-in-pack functionality."
msgstr ""
"Inställningen *Ställ in emballagetyp* måste aktiveras för alla processer som "
"kräver funktionalitet för emballage i emballage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:27
msgid ""
"Open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Operation Types`. "
"The :guilabel:`Operation Types` page opens. Open an operation type."
msgstr ""
"Öppna :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> Processtyper`. "
"Sidan :guilabel:`Processtyper` öppnas. Öppna en processtyp."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:30
msgid ""
"On the operation type form, in the :guilabel:`Packages` section, "
"select :guilabel:`Set Package Type`."
msgstr ""
"På formuläret för processtyp, i sektionen :guilabel:`Emballage`, "
"välj :guilabel:`Ställ in emballagetyp`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Set Package Type` is enabled for the `Receipts` operation type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ställ in emballagetyp` är aktiverad för processtypen "
"`Inleveranser`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:0
msgid "Update the Set Package Type setting on the operation type form."
msgstr ""
"Uppgradera inställningen Ställ in emballagetyp på formuläret för processtyp."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:40
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:125
msgid "Create package types"
msgstr "Skapa emballagetyper"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:42
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:127
msgid ""
"Create package types by navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Package Types`, in order to set custom dimensions and "
"weight limits. This feature is mainly used to calculate package weights for "
"shipping costs."
msgstr ""
"Skapa pakettyper genom att navigera till :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Package Types`, för att ställa in anpassade mått och "
"viktgränser. Denna funktion används främst för att beräkna paketvikter för "
"fraktkostnader."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:46
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:135
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Package Types` list, clicking :guilabel:`New` opens a "
"blank package type form. The fields of the form are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Om du klickar på :guilabel:`New` i listan :guilabel:`Packagetyper` öppnas "
"ett tomt formulär för pakettyp. Fälten i formuläret är följande:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Package Type` (required): Define the package type's name."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Emballagetyp` (obligatorisk): Ange emballagetypen namn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Size`: Define the package dimensions in millimeters (mm). The "
"fields, from left to right, define the Length, Width, and Height."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Storlek`: Ange emballagets dimensioner i millimeter (mm). Fälten, "
"från vänster till höger, anger längd, bredd och höjd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Weight`: weight of an empty package (e.g., an empty box, pallet)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vikt`: vikt av ett tomt emballage (t.ex. en tom låda, pall)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:55
msgid ""
"Odoo calculates the package's weight by adding the weight of the empty "
"package plus the weight of the items, which can be found in "
"the :guilabel:`Weight` field, in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, of each "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Odoo beräknar emballagets vikt genom att lägga till vikten av det tomma "
"emballaget plus vikten av artiklarna, som kan hittas i "
"fältet :guilabel:`Vikt` på fliken :guilabel:`Lager` i varje produktformulär."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:59
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:148
msgid ":guilabel:`Max Weight`: maximum shipping weight allowed in the package."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Max Weight`: högsta tillåtna fraktvikt i paketet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:149
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Barcode`: Define a barcode to identify the package type from a "
"scan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Streckkod`: Definiera en streckkod för att identifiera "
"emballagetypen från en skanning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sequence Prefix`: Specify a prefix to use when a new package name "
"is created by Odoo."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nummerserieprefix`: Ange ett prefix som ska användas när ett nytt "
"emballagenamn skapas av Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:64
msgid ""
"Use `PAL` for the `Pallet` package type. When the first package of the "
"`Pallet` type is created, it is named `PAL0000001`."
msgstr ""
"Använd `PAL` för emballagetypen `Pall`. När det första emballaget av typen "
"`Pall` skapas får det namnet `PAL0000001`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: Specify a company to make the package type available "
"only within that company. Leave the field blank if it is available at all "
"companies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Företag`: Ange ett företag för att göra emballagetypen "
"tillgänglig endast inom det företaget. Lämna fältet tomt om det är "
"tillgängligt för alla företag."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:152
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Carrier`: Specify the intended shipping carrier for this package "
"type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Transportföretag`: Ange det avsedda transportföretaget för denna "
"emballagetyp."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:70
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Carrier Code`: Define a code that is linked to the package type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Transportföretagskod`: Definiera en kod som är länkad till "
"emballagetypen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:None
msgid "Create a custom package type."
msgstr "Skapa en anpassad emballagetyp."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:76
msgid "Pack-in-pack process"
msgstr "Emballage-i-emballage-process"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:78
msgid ""
"After :guilabel:`Set Package Type` is enabled in the operation type form, "
"pack-in-pack can be used from that operation type."
msgstr ""
"Efter att :guilabel:`Ange emballagetyp` har aktiverats i processformuläret "
"kan emballage-i-emballage användas från den processtypen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:81
msgid ""
"Open the operation type from the :guilabel:`Operations` menu. The list of "
"operations for that operation type displays. Open an operation from that "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Öppna processtypen från menyn :guilabel:`Processer`. Listan över processer "
"för den processtypen visas. Öppna en process från den listan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:84
msgid ""
"To put the contents of a line into a single package, click "
"the :guilabel:`Details` link on the far right of the product line."
msgstr ""
"För att lägga innehållet i en rad i ett enda emballage, klicka på "
"länken :guilabel:`Detaljer` längst till höger på produktserien."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:None
msgid ""
"Use the Details link to open the Detailed Operations window and specify a "
"package."
msgstr ""
"Använd länken Detaljer för att öppna fönstret Detaljerade processer och ange "
"ett emballage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:90
msgid ""
"The *Detailed Operations* window opens. In this window, specify "
"a :guilabel:`Store to` location, the name of the :guilabel:`Destination "
"Package`, and the :guilabel:`Quantity` of items to be put in that package. "
"To break the inventory into multiple packages, click the :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` link; be sure that the :guilabel:`Quantity` of each line adds up to "
"the total :guilabel:`Demand`. Click :guilabel:`Save` to create the package "
"in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Fönstret *Detaljerade processer* öppnas. I detta fönster anger du "
"en :guilabel:`Lagra till`-plats, namnet på :guilabel:`Destinationsemballage` "
"och :guilabel:`Kvantitet` av artiklar som ska läggas i det emballaget. För "
"att dela upp lagret i flera emballage klickar du på länken :guilabel:`Lägg "
"till en rad`; se till att :guilabel:`Kvantitet` för varje rad summerar till "
"den totala :guilabel:`Efterfrågan`. Klicka på :guilabel:`Spara` för att "
"skapa emballaget i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:None
msgid "Specify a Destination Package in the Detailed Operations form."
msgstr "Ange ett destinationsemballage i formuläret Detaljerade processer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:99
msgid "Repeat this process for all product lines on the operation form."
msgstr "Upprepa denna process för alla produktserier på processformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:101
msgid ""
"Alternatively, click the :guilabel:`Put in Pack` button on the operation "
"form to put all items with a :guilabel:`Quantity` greater than `0.00` into a "
"package. The *Put in Pack* pop-up window opens."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Lägg i emballage` på "
"processformuläret för att lägga alla artiklar med en :guilabel:`Kvantitet` "
"större än `0.00` i ett emballage. Popup-fönstret *Lägg i emballage* öppnas."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:104
msgid ""
"In the *Put in Pack* window, specify a :guilabel:`Package Type` "
"and :guilabel:`Package`, or leave the :guilabel:`Package` field blank to "
"create a new package. Then click the :guilabel:`Put in Pack` button. The "
"package name appears in the product line's :guilabel:`Packages` field."
msgstr ""
"I fönstret *Lägg i emballage* anger du en :guilabel:`Emballagetyp` "
"och :guilabel:`Emballage`, eller lämnar fältet :guilabel:`Emballage` tomt "
"för att skapa ett nytt emballage. Klicka sedan på knappen :guilabel:`Lägg i "
"emballage`. Emballagenamnet visas i produktseriens "
"fält :guilabel:`Emballage`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:None
msgid "Specify a Package Type and, optionally, a package name."
msgstr "Ange en emballagetyp och, valfritt, ett emballagenamn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:112
msgid ""
"A business has placed an order for `20` units each of `Apple Juice Cans`, "
"`Orange Juice Cans`, `Sparkling Water Cans`, and `Soda Cans`. When the order "
"arrives, each product arrives in its own box of 20 cans."
msgstr ""
"Ett företag har lagt en beställning på `20` enheter vardera av "
"`Äppeljuiceburkar`, `Apelsinjuiceburkar`, `Kolsyrade vattenburkar` och "
"`Läskburkar`. När beställningen anländer kommer varje produkt i sin egen "
"låda med 20 burkar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:116
msgid ""
"The warehouse manager specifies a separate package for each product line on "
"the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Lagerchef specificerar ett separat emballage för varje produktserie på "
"inleveransen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:0
msgid "Four packages are created on the receipt form."
msgstr "Fyra emballage skapas på inleveransformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:121
msgid ""
"Then, to organize all packages into a single larger unit (for example, to "
"package multiple cases of soda into a pallet), click the :guilabel:`Put in "
"Pack` button. After closing the *Put in Pack* window, "
"the :guilabel:`Packages` field for the product lines in the greater package "
"updates with the new package name."
msgstr ""
"För att sedan organisera alla emballage till en enda större enhet (till "
"exempel för att förpacka flera backar läsk på en pall), klicka på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Lägg i emballage`. Efter att *Lägg i emballage*-fönstret "
"stängts uppdateras fältet :guilabel:`Emballage` för produktserierna i det "
"större emballaget med det nya emballagenamnet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:127
msgid ""
"Continuing the example from above, the warehouse manager wants to package "
"all of the products onto a single pallet for storage in the warehouse. They "
"click the :guilabel:`Put in Pack` button, then in the *Put in Pack* window, "
"they specify `Pallet` as the :guilabel:`Package Type`. "
"The :guilabel:`Packages` field for all product lines updates to show the "
"pallet package name, `PAL0000001`."
msgstr ""
"För att fortsätta exemplet ovan vill lagerchefen förpacka alla produkter på "
"en enda pall för förvaring i lagret. De klickar på knappen :guilabel:`Lägg i "
"emballage`, sedan i fönstret *Lägg i emballage* specificerar de `Pall` "
"som :guilabel:`Emballagetyp`. Fältet :guilabel:`Emballage` för alla "
"produktserier uppdateras för att visa pallembalagets namn, `PAL0000001`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:0
msgid "The Packages field updates with a new package name."
msgstr "Emballagefältet uppdateras med ett nytt emballagenamn."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:136
msgid ""
"Be sure to :guilabel:`Validate` the operation to process its move in "
"inventory."
msgstr ""
"Se till att :guilabel:`Validera` processen för att behandla dess transport i "
"lagret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:139
msgid "Viewing the packages in an operation"
msgstr "Visa emballage i en process"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:141
msgid ""
"To view the packages created from an operation, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cubes` :guilabel:`Packages` smart button at the top of the operation form. "
"By default, this list is filtered by the :guilabel:`Main Packages`, or the "
"largest package assigned to the operation. To view all packages, remove "
"the :guilabel:`Main Packages` filter."
msgstr ""
"För att visa emballage som skapats från en process, klicka på smart "
"knapp :icon:`fa-cubes` :guilabel:`Emballage` längst upp på "
"processformuläret. Som standard filtreras denna lista "
"efter :guilabel:`Huvudemballage`, eller det största emballaget som "
"tilldelats processen. För att visa alla emballage, ta bort "
"filtret :guilabel:`Huvudemballage`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:None
msgid "Show all packages on the Packages list."
msgstr "Visa alla emballage i emballagelistan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:150
msgid "Removing packages from parent packages"
msgstr "Ta bort emballage från överordnade emballage"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:152
msgid ""
"To remove packages from parent packages, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cubes` :guilabel:`Packages` smart button at the top of the operation form. "
"By default, this list is filtered by the :guilabel:`Main Packages`, or the "
"largest package assigned to the operation. To view all packages, remove "
"the :guilabel:`Main Packages` filter."
msgstr ""
"För att ta bort emballage från överordnade emballage, klicka på smart "
"knapp :icon:`fa-cubes` :guilabel:`Emballage` längst upp på "
"processformuläret. Som standard filtreras denna lista "
"efter :guilabel:`Huvudemballage`, eller det största emballaget som "
"tilldelats processen. För att visa alla emballage, ta bort "
"filtret :guilabel:`Huvudemballage`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:157
msgid ""
"Select the check boxes next to the packages that you want to remove, then "
"click the :guilabel:`Remove` button."
msgstr ""
"Kryssa för rutorna bredvid de emballage du vill ta bort och klicka sedan på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Ta bort`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:161
msgid "Viewing packages in inventory"
msgstr "Visa emballage i lager"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:163
msgid ""
"Open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> Packages`. All packages "
"in inventory are listed here."
msgstr ""
"Öppna :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Produkter --> Emballage`. Alla emballage "
"i lagret listas här."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:166
msgid ""
"To view the contents of a package, open the package from the list of "
"packages. The products in the package, including the child packages they are "
"stored in, are listed on the package form."
msgstr ""
"För att visa innehållet i ett emballage, öppna emballaget från listan över "
"emballage. Produkterna i emballaget, inklusive de underordnade emballage de "
"förvaras i, listas på emballageformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/pack_in_pack.rst:None
msgid "Child packages are listed on the package reference form."
msgstr "Underordnade emballage listas på formuläret för spårningsnummer."

