msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bpost Account Number` (required field): enter the company's "
"unique :ref:`account ID <inventory/shipping_receiving/bpost-account>` from "
"the Bpost website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bpost-kontonummer` (obligatoriskt fält): ange företagets "
"unika :ref:`konto-ID <inventory/shipping_receiving/bpost-account>` från "
