"metoden på alla företag. Detta fält visas endast i databaser med flera "
"företag."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Routes`: select the applicable routes to define different "
"delivery methods, such as standard or express shipping, based on varying "
"lead times. This field only appears when you have enabled multi-step routes "
"in your inventory configuration settings. For more information, refer to "
"the :ref:`Set routes on shipping method <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"shipping-route>` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rutter`: välj tillämpliga rutter för att definiera olika "
"leveransmetoder, såsom standard- eller expressleverans, baserat på "
"varierande ledtider. Detta fält visas endast när du har aktiverat "
"flerstegsrutter i dina lagerinstllningar. För mer information, se "
"avsnittet :ref:`Ställ in rutter på transportmetod <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/shipping-route>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product` (*Required field*): the product listed on "
