msgid "Example of shipping products configured in Odoo."
msgstr "Exempel på fraktprodukter som konfigurerats i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:199
msgid ""
"Sendcloud does not provide test keys when a company tests the sending of a "
"package in Odoo. This means if a package is created, the configured "
"Sendcloud account will be charged, unless the associated package is "
"cancelled within 24 hours of creation."
msgstr ""
"Sendcloud tillhandahåller inte testnycklar när ett företag testar att skicka "
"ett paket i Odoo. Detta innebär att om ett paket skapas kommer det "
"konfigurerade Sendcloud-kontot att debiteras, såvida inte det tillhörande "
"paketet annulleras inom 24 timmar efter skapandet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:203
msgid ""
"Odoo has a built-in layer of protection against unwanted charges when using "
"test environments. Within a test environment, if a shipping method is used "
"to create labels, then those labels are immediately cancelled after the "
"creation — this occurs automatically. The test and production environment "
"settings can be toggled back and forth from their respective smart buttons."
msgstr ""
"Odoo har ett inbyggt lager av skydd mot oönskade avgifter när du använder "
"testmiljöer. I en testmiljö, om en leveransmetod används för att skapa "
"etiketter, annulleras dessa etiketter omedelbart efter skapandet - detta "
"sker automatiskt. Inställningarna för test- och produktionsmiljön kan växlas "
"fram och tillbaka från respektive smartknapp."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:213
msgid ""
"To use Sendcloud to generate shipping labels, the following information "
"**must** be filled out accurately and completely in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"För att använda Sendcloud för att generera fraktetiketter måste följande "
"information **fyllas i korrekt och fullständigt i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:216
msgid ""
"**Customer information**: when creating a quotation, ensure the "
"selected :guilabel:`Customer` has a valid phone number, email address, and "
"shipping address."
msgstr ""
"**Kundinformation**: När du skapar en offert ska du se till att den "
"valda :guilabel:`Kunden` har ett giltigt telefonnummer, e-postadress och "
"leveransadress."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:223
msgid ""
"**Product weight**: ensure all products in an order have a "
"specified :guilabel:`Weight` in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of their "
"product form. Refer to the :ref:`Product weight section <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` of this article for detailed "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Produktvikt**: se till att alla produkter i en order har en "
"angiven :guilabel:`Weight` på fliken :guilabel:`Inventory` i "
"produktformuläret. Se avsnittet :ref:`Produktvikt <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` i den här artikeln för detaljerade "
"instruktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:227
msgid ""
"**Warehouse address**: ensure the warehouse name and address in Odoo match "
"the :ref:`previously defined warehouse <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-warehouse-config>` in the Sendcloud setup. For details on "
"warehouse configuration in Odoo, refer to the :ref:`warehouse configuration "
"section <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` of the "
"third-party shipping documentation."
msgstr ""
"**Lageradress**: se till att lagernamnet och adressen i Odoo "
"matchar :ref:`det tidigare definierade lagret <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-warehouse-config>` i Sendcloud-inställningen. Mer information om "
"lagerkonfiguration i Odoo finns i avsnittet :ref:`Lagerkonfiguration "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` i dokumentationen "
"för tredjepartssändningar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:234
msgid "Generate labels with Sendcloud"
msgstr "Generera etiketter med Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:236
msgid ""
"When creating a quotation in Odoo, add shipping and a :guilabel:`Sendcloud "
"shipping product`. Then, :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery. Shipping label "
"documents are automatically generated in the chatter, which include the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"När du skapar en offert i Odoo, lägg till frakt och en :guilabel:`Sendcloud "
"fraktprodukt`. Sedan :guilabel:`Validera` leveransen. Fraktetikettdokument "
"genereras automatiskt i chattern, som inkluderar följande:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:241
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Return label(s)` if the Sendcloud connector is configured for "
"returns."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Returetikett(er)` om Sendcloud-kontakten är konfigurerad för "
"returer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:242
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customs document(s)` should the destination country require them."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tullhandling(ar)` om destinationslandet kräver detta."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:247
msgid ""
"When return labels are created, Sendcloud automatically charges the "
"configured Sendcloud account."
msgstr ""
"När returetiketter skapas debiterar Sendcloud automatiskt det konfigurerade "
"Sendcloud-kontot."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:250
msgid "Shipping rules"
msgstr "Regler för frakt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:252
msgid ""
"Optionally, create shipping rules to automatically generate shipping labels "
"tailored to different product needs. For example, a shipping rule can be "
"created for customers shipping expensive jewelry items to purchase insurance."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du skapa leveransregler för att automatiskt generera "
"fraktetiketter som är anpassade till olika produktbehov. Till exempel kan en "
"leveransregel skapas för kunder som skickar dyra smycken för att köpa "
"försäkring."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:257
msgid ""
"Shipping rules do **not** affect :ref:`shipping rate calculations <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>`, and are only used to improve the "
"process of :doc:`generating shipping labels <labels>`."
msgstr ""
"Leveransregler påverkar **inte** :ref:`beräkningar av fraktsatser <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>`, och används endast för att förbättra "
"processen för :doc:`generering av fraktetiketter <labels>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:261
msgid ""
"To use shipping rules, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Delivery: Shipping Methods`, and select the intended "
"`Sendcloud` shipping method."
msgstr ""
"För att använda leveransregler, navigera till :menuselection:`Inventory app "
"--> Configuration --> Delivery: Shipping Methods`, och välj den avsedda "
"leveransmetoden `Sendcloud`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:264
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Configuration` tab, in "
"the :guilabel:`OPTIONS` section, choose the kind of shipments the shipping "
"rules apply to, via the :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud shipping rules` field."
msgstr ""
"Under fliken :guilabel:`Sendcloud Configuration`, i "
"avsnittet :guilabel:`OPTIONS`, väljer du vilken typ av försändelser som "
"leveransreglerna gäller för via fältet :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud shipping "
"rules`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:268
msgid ""
"From here, choose either: :guilabel:`Shipping` to "
"customers, :guilabel:`Returns` from customers, or :guilabel:`Both`."
msgstr ""
"Här väljer du antingen: :guilabel:`Shipping` till "
"kunder, :guilabel:`Returns` från kunder eller :guilabel:`Both`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Use Shipping Rules field."
msgstr "Använd fältet Leveransregler."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:275
msgid ""
"Then, in the Sendcloud website, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Shipping rules`. Create a new shipping rule by clicking :guilabel:`Create "
"New`."
msgstr ""
"Navigera sedan på Sendcloud-webbplatsen till :menuselection:`Inställningar --"
"> Leveransregler`. Skapa en ny leveransregel genom att klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Create New`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:278
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Actions` section, set a :guilabel:`Condition` to determine "
"when the rule applies. Then, configure what to do when packages meet the "
"condition."
msgstr ""
"I avsnittet :guilabel:`Actions` anger du ett :guilabel:`Condition` för att "
"avgöra när regeln ska tillämpas. Konfigurera sedan vad som ska göras när "
"paket uppfyller villkoret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:282
msgid ""
"`Create shipping rules on Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-smart-"
"shipping-rules>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Create shipping rules on Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-smart-"
"shipping-rules>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:289
msgid "Shipment is too heavy"
msgstr "Sändningen är för tung"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:291
msgid ""
"If the shipment is too heavy for the Sendcloud service that is configured, "
"then the weight is split to simulate multiple packages. Products will need "
"to be put in different :guilabel:`Packages` to :guilabel:`Validate` the "
"transfer and generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Om försändelsen är för tung för den Sendcloud-tjänst som är konfigurerad, "
"delas vikten upp för att simulera flera paket. Produkterna måste läggas i "
"olika :guilabel:`Packages` för att :guilabel:`Validera` överföringen och "
"generera etiketter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:295
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rules` can also be set up in Sendcloud to use other shipping "
"methods when the weight is too heavy. However, note that these rules will "
"not apply to the shipping price calculation on the calculation on the sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rules` kan också ställas in i Sendcloud för att använda andra "
"fraktmetoder när vikten är för tung. Observera dock att dessa regler inte "
"kommer att gälla för fraktprisberäkningen på beräkningen på "
"försäljningsordern."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:300
msgid "Personal carrier contract"
msgstr "Personligt transportavtal"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:302
msgid ""
"Use custom prices from a direct carrier contract, via CSV upload, by first "
"logging into Sendcloud, navigating to :menuselection:`Settings --> Carriers "
"--> My contracts`, and then selecting the intended contract."
msgstr ""
"Använd anpassade priser från ett direkt transportavtal, via CSV-uppladdning, "
"genom att först logga in på Sendcloud, navigera "
"till :menuselection:`Inställningar --> Transportörer --> Mina avtal`, och "
"sedan välja det avsedda avtalet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Navigate to the contracts section in Sendcloud."
msgstr "Navigera till avtalssektionen i Sendcloud."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:310
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Contract prices` section, click :guilabel:`Download "
"CSV` and fill out the contract prices in the :guilabel:`price` column of the "
"CSV file template."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :guilabel:`Download CSV` under avsnittet :guilabel:`Contract "
"prices` och fyll i kontraktspriserna i kolumnen :guilabel:`price` i CSV-"
"filmallen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:314
msgid ""
"Ensure the CSV file includes the correct prices to avoid any inaccuracies."
msgstr ""
"Se till att CSV-filen innehåller korrekta priser för att undvika "
"felaktigheter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Show sample contract CSV from Sendcloud, highlighting the price column."
msgstr ""
"Visa exempel på kontrakt CSV från Sendcloud, med pris kolumnen markerad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:320
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Upload` the completed CSV file to Sendcloud, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save these prices`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ladda upp` den färdiga CSV-filen till Sendcloud och klicka sedan "
"på :guilabel:`Spara dessa priser`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:323
msgid ""
"`Sendcloud: How to upload contract prices with carriers <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/5163547066004>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Sendcloud: Hur man laddar upp avtalspriser med operatörer <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/5163547066004>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:329
msgid ""
"Many carriers have several measures for weight. There is the actual weight "
"of the products in the parcel, and there is the *volumetric weight* "
"(:dfn:`Volumetric weight is the volume that a package occupies when in "
"transit. In other words it is the physical size of a package`)."
msgstr ""
"Många transportörer har flera olika viktmått. Det finns den faktiska vikten "
"av produkterna i paketet, och det finns den *volymetriska vikten* "
"(:dfn:`Volymetrisk vikt är den volym som ett paket upptar när det är i "
"transit. Med andra ord är det paketets fysiska storlek`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:334
msgid ""
"Check to see if selected carrier(s) already have defined formulas to compute "
"the volumetric weight."
msgstr ""
"Kontrollera om valda transportörer redan har definierade formler för att "
"beräkna volymvikten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:338
msgid ""
"`Sendcloud: How to calculate & automate parcel volumetric weight <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/ hc/en-us/articles/360059644051-How-to-calculate-"
"automate-parcel-volumetric-weight>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Sendcloud: Hur man beräknar och automatiserar paketets volymetriska vikt "
"<https://support.sendcloud.com/ hc/en-us/articles/360059644051-How-to-"
"calculate-automate-parcel-volumetric-weight>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:342
msgid "Unable to calculate shipping rate"
msgstr "Kan inte beräkna fraktkostnad"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:344
msgid ""
"First, verify that the product being shipped has a weight that is supported "
"by the selected shipping method. If this is set, then verify that the "
"destination country (from the customer address) is supported by the carrier. "
"The country of origin (warehouse address) should also be supported by the "
"carrier."
msgstr ""
"Kontrollera först att den produkt som ska skickas har en vikt som stöds av "
"den valda leveransmetoden. Om detta är inställt, kontrollera sedan att "
"destinationslandet (från kundadressen) stöds av transportören. "
"Ursprungslandet (lageradressen) bör också stödjas av transportören."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:3
msgid "Shiprocket integration"
msgstr "Shiprocket-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:5
msgid ""
"Shiprocket is an Indian service that allows users to connect with multiple "
"carriers, like Delhivery, Blue Dart, DTDC, India Post, Xpressbees, and more. "
"To manage Shiprocket shipments to clients directly within Odoo, it must "
"first be configured."
msgstr ""
"Shiprocket är en indisk tjänst som gör det möjligt för användare att ansluta "
"till flera transportörer, som Delhivery, Blue Dart, DTDC, India Post, "
"Xpressbees och fler. För att hantera Shiprocket-transporter till kunder "
"direkt inom Odoo måste det först konfigureras."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:11
msgid ""
":ref:`Create a Shiprocket account <inventory/shiprocket/account-setup>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Skapa ett Shiprocket-konto <inventory/shiprocket/account-setup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:12
msgid ":ref:`Create an API user <inventory/shiprocket/api-user>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Skapa en programmeringsgränssnitt-användare <inventory/shiprocket/api-"
"user>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:13
msgid ":ref:`Create a sales channel <inventory/shiprocket/sales-channel>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Skapa en försäljningskanal <inventory/shiprocket/sales-channel>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`Enable couriers <inventory/shiprocket/enable-couriers>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Aktivera transportörer <inventory/shiprocket/enable-couriers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:15
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable the Shiprocket connector in Odoo <inventory/shiprocket/enable>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Aktivera Shiprocket-anslutningen i Odoo <inventory/shiprocket/enable>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:16
msgid ""
":ref:`Configure the delivery method in Odoo <inventory/shiprocket/"
"configure>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Konfigurera leveransmetoden i Odoo <inventory/shiprocket/configure>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:18
msgid ""
"Upon completion, it is possible to calculate shipping costs based on package "
"size and weight, have the charges applied directly to a Shiprocket account, "
"and automatically print Shiprocket tracking labels in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"När detta är klart är det möjligt att beräkna transportkostnader baserat på "
"emballagestorlek och vikt, få avgifterna tillämpade direkt på ett Shiprocket-"
"konto och automatiskt skriva ut Shiprocket-spårningsetiketter i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:27
msgid ""
"To begin, go to the `Shiprocket website <https://app.shiprocket.in/"
"newlogin>`_ to create or log into the company's Shiprocket account."
msgstr ""
"För att börja, gå till `Shiprocket-hemsidan <https://app.shiprocket.in/"
"newlogin>`_ för att skapa eller logga in på företagets Shiprocket-konto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:30
msgid "Follow the website's steps to complete registration."
msgstr "Följ hemsidans steg för att slutföra registreringen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:35
msgid "Create API user"
msgstr "Skapa programmeringsgränssnittsanvändare"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:37
msgid ""
"On the Shiprocket *Homepage*, open the :menuselection:`Settings` menu. In "
"the *Additional Settings* section, navigate to the :menuselection:`API "
"Users` page."
msgstr ""
"På Shiprockets *startsida* öppnar du menyn :menuselection:`Inställningar`. I "
"sektionen *Additional Settings* navigerar du till sidan :menuselection:`API "
"Users`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:40
msgid ""
"On the *API Users* page, click the :guilabel:`+ Add New API User` button. In "
"the *Add New User* window, specify an :guilabel:`Email ID`. Open "
"the :guilabel:`Select Modules to Access` menu and select :guilabel:`Orders "
"(create, "
"update)`, :guilabel:`Settings`, :guilabel:`Shipments`, :guilabel:`Listings`, "
"and :guilabel:`Courier`, then click :guilabel:`Apply`. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Create User` to add the user."
msgstr ""
"På sidan *API Users* klickar du på knappen :guilabel:`+ Add New API User`. I "
"fönstret *Add New User* anger du ett :guilabel:`Email ID`. Öppna "
"menyn :guilabel:`Select Modules to Access` och välj :guilabel:`Orders "
"(create, "
"update)`, :guilabel:`Settings`, :guilabel:`Shipments`, :guilabel:`Listings` "
"och :guilabel:`Courier`, klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Apply`. Slutligen "
"klickar du på :guilabel:`Create User` för att lägga till användaren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:46
msgid "Copy the API password from the *Your API Password* window."
msgstr ""
"Kopiera programmeringsgränssnittslösenordet från fönstret *Your API "
"Password*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click the Copy token icon to copy the password to the device's clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på ikonen Copy token för att kopiera lösenordet till enhetens urklipp."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:54
msgid "Create sales channel"
msgstr "Skapa försäljningskanal"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:56
msgid ""
"From the sidebar, navigate to :menuselection:`Setup & Manage --> Channels`. "
"On the *Sales Channels* page, click :guilabel:`Connect New Channel`. In the "
"*Shopping Carts* section, click the :guilabel:`Add` button under the "
"*Manual* heading. The *Manual* settings page opens."
msgstr ""
"Från sidofältet navigerar du till :menuselection:`Setup & Manage --> "
"Channels`. På sidan *Sales Channels* klickar du på :guilabel:`Connect New "
"Channel`. I sektionen *Shopping Carts* klickar du på knappen :guilabel:`Add` "
"under rubriken *Manual*. Sidan *Manual* settings öppnas."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:60
msgid ""
"Specify a :guilabel:`Channel Name`, such as `Odoo`. Click :guilabel:`Save "
"Channel & Test Connection`."
msgstr ""
"Ange ett :guilabel:`Channel Name`, till exempel `Odoo`. Klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Save Channel & Test Connection`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Create a sales channel."
msgstr "Skapa en försäljningskanal."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:69
msgid "Configure couriers"
msgstr "Konfigurera kurirer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:71
msgid ""
"From the sidebar, navigate to :menuselection:`Setup & Manage --> Courier`. "
"On the *Courier Selection* page, enable or disable shipping couriers."
msgstr ""
"Från sidofältet navigerar du till :menuselection:`Setup & Manage --> "
"Courier`. På sidan *Courier Selection* aktiverar eller avaktiverar du "
"fraktkurirer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Toggle couriers to select them on the Courier Selection page."
msgstr "Växla kurirer för att välja dem på sidan Courier Selection."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:77
msgid ""
"Open the :menuselection:`Courier Priority` page. Set a priority ranking to "
"which orders are assigned and click :guilabel:`Save`. The courier is "
"selected in Odoo based on this priority. For example, "
"if :guilabel:`Cheapest` is selected, the most cost-effective courier is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Öppna sidan :menuselection:`Courier Priority`. Ställ in en "
"prioritetsrangordning som order tilldelas efter och klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Spara`. Kuriren väljs i Odoo baserat på denna prioritet. Om "
"till exempel :guilabel:`Cheapest` väljs, väljs den mest kostnadseffektiva "
"kuriren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:84
msgid "Enable connector"
msgstr "Aktivera anslutning"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:86
msgid ""
"The *Shiprocket Connector* must be enabled before a shipping method can be "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"*Shiprocket Connector* måste aktiveras innan en fraktmetod kan konfigureras."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:88
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"In the *Shipping Connectors* section, enable :guilabel:`Shiprocket "
"Connector`, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Navigera till :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> "
"Inställningar`. I sektionen *Shipping Connectors* aktiverar "
"du :guilabel:`Shiprocket Connector` och klickar sedan på :guilabel:`Spara`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:96
msgid ""
"Configure the Shiprocket delivery method in Odoo by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Delivery Methods`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurera Shiprocket-leveransmetoden i Odoo genom att gå "
"till :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> Delivery Methods`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:99
msgid ""
"On the *Delivery Methods* page, open the :guilabel:`ShipRocket Domestic` "
"shipping method, or click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"På sidan *Delivery Methods* öppnar du fraktmetoden :guilabel:`ShipRocket "
"Domestic` eller klickar på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:102
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Provider` field, select :guilabel:`Shiprocket` from the "
"list of providers. Doing so reveals the *Shiprocket Configuration* tab at "
"the bottom of the form, where Shiprocket credentials are entered."
msgstr ""
"I fältet :guilabel:`Leverantör` väljer du :guilabel:`Shiprocket` från listan "
"över leverantörer. Detta visar fliken *Shiprocket Configuration* längst ner "
"i formuläret, där Shiprocket-uppgifter anges."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:106
msgid ""
"For details on configuring the other fields on the shipping method, such "
"as :guilabel:`Delivery Product`, refer to the :doc:`new_delivery_method` "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"För detaljer om hur man konfigurerar övriga fält för fraktmetoden, "
"såsom :guilabel:`Leveransprodukt`, se :doc:`new_delivery_method`-"
"dokumentationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:110
msgid ""
"To generate Shiprocket shipping labels through Odoo, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Integration Level` option is set to :guilabel:`Get Rate and "
"Create Shipment`."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa Shiprocket-fraktsedlar via Odoo, se till att "
"alternativet :guilabel:`Integrationsnivå` är inställt på :guilabel:`Hämta "
"anrop och skapa försändelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:114
msgid "Shiprocket Configuration tab"
msgstr "Fliken Shiprocket-konfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:116
msgid ""
"Enter the API user email address in the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Email` field. "
"Enter the API password for the user in the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Password` "
"field. Click the :guilabel:`Test Connection` link."
msgstr ""
"Ange användarens e-postadress för programmeringsgränssnittet i "
"fältet :guilabel:`Shiprocket-e-post`. Ange programmeringsgränssnittets "
"lösenord för användaren i fältet :guilabel:`Shiprocket-lösenord`. Klicka på "
"länken :guilabel:`Testa anslutning`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:120
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Pickup Request` to send a pickup request when a delivery "
"order is validated."
msgstr ""
"Välj :guilabel:`Avhämtningsförfrågan` för att skicka en avhämtningsförfrågan "
"när en leveransorder valideras."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:122
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Generate Manifest` to generate a shipping manifest and "
"streamline the pickup process."
msgstr ""
"Välj :guilabel:`Skapa manifest` för att skapa ett fraktmanifest och "
"effektivisera avhämtningsprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:125
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Package Type` field, select a package dimension to use for "
"shipments."
msgstr ""
"I fältet :guilabel:`Emballagetyp`, välj en emballagedimension att använda "
"för försändelser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:127
msgid ""
"To retrieve the list of supported Shiprocket couriers, click the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(Sync Couriers from Shiprocket)` icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Couriers` field. Select the couriers to use in "
"the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Couriers` field. If this field is left blank, Odoo "
"will select the first courier based on the :ref:`courier priority <inventory/"
"shiprocket/enable-couriers>` set in the Shiprocket portal."
msgstr ""
"För att hämta listan över Shiprocket-transporter som stöds, klicka på "
"ikonen :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(Synkronisera transporter från "
"Shiprocket)` bredvid fältet :guilabel:`Shiprocket-transporter`. Välj de "
"transporter som ska användas i fältet :guilabel:`Shiprocket-transporter`. Om "
"detta fält lämnas tomt kommer Odoo att välja den första transporten baserat "
"på :ref:`transportprioritet <inventory/shiprocket/enable-couriers>` som "
"angetts i Shiprocket-portalen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:133
msgid ""
"To retrieve the list of Shiprocket channels, click the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(Sync Channel from Shiprocket)` icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Channel` field. In the :guilabel:`Shiprocket "
"Channel` field, select the sales channel that was created in "
"the :ref:`inventory/shiprocket/sales-channel` step."
msgstr ""
"För att hämta listan över Shiprocket-kanaler, klicka på ikonen :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(Synkronisera kanal från Shiprocket)` bredvid "
"fältet :guilabel:`Shiprocket-kanal`. I fältet :guilabel:`Shiprocket-kanal`, "
"välj den försäljningskanal som skapades i :ref:`inventory/shiprocket/sales-"
"channel`-steget."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Complete the fields of the form to make the shipping method available."
msgstr "Fyll i fältens formulär för att göra fraktmetoden tillgänglig."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:142
msgid "Availability tab"
msgstr "Fliken Tillgänglighet"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:144
msgid ""
"Use the *Availability* tab to specify the :guilabel:`Countries` to which the "
"shipping method should apply. Shiprocket supports deliveries to over 220 "
"countries."
msgstr ""
"Använd fliken *Tillgänglighet* för att ange de :guilabel:`länder` som "
"fraktmetoden ska gälla för. Shiprocket stöder leveranser till över 220 "
"länder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:150
msgid ""
"To use Shiprocket to generate shipping labels, the following information "
"**must** be filled out accurately and completely in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"För att använda Shiprocket för att skapa fraktsedlar **måste** följande "
"information fyllas i korrekt och fullständigt i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:156
msgid ""
"To verify, select the :guilabel:`Customer` field to open their contact page. "
"Add their shipping address in the :guilabel:`Contact` field, along with "
"their :guilabel:`Mobile` number and :guilabel:`Email` address."
msgstr ""
"För att verifiera, välj fältet :guilabel:`Kund` för att öppna deras "
"kontaktsida. Lägg till deras leveransadress i fältet :guilabel:`Kontakt`, "
"tillsammans med deras :guilabel:`mobilnummer` och :guilabel:`e-postadress`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:159
msgid ""
"**Product weight**: Ensure all products in a delivery order have a "
"specified :guilabel:`Weight` in the *Inventory* tab of their product form. "
"Refer to the :ref:`inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-weight` "
"documentation for detailed instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Produktvikt**: Se till att alla produkter i en leveransorder har en "
"angiven :guilabel:`vikt` i fliken *Lager* i deras produktformulär. "
"Se :ref:`inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-weight`-dokumentationen för "
"detaljerade instruktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:162
msgid ""
"**Warehouse address**: By default all packages are sent from the specified "
"address in the warehouse. Make sure to set the :guilabel:`Address` in the "
"warehouse form with a valid phone number and email address."
msgstr ""
"**Lageradress**: Som standard skickas alla emballage från den angivna "
"adressen i lagret. Se till att ange :guilabel:`adressen` i lagerformuläret "
"med ett giltigt telefonnummer och e-postadress."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:167
msgid "Generate a Shiprocket label"
msgstr "Skapa en Shiprocket-etikett"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:169
msgid ""
"When creating a quotation in Odoo, add the Shiprocket shipping method by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Add shipping` button."
msgstr ""
"När du skapar en offert i Odoo, lägg till Shiprocket-fraktmetoden genom att "
"klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Lägg till frakt`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:172
msgid ""
"In the *Add a shipping method* pop-up window, select :guilabel:`Shiprocket` "
"in the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` field. Calculate the shipping rate by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Get rate`. Finally, click :guilabel:`Add` to include the "
"shipping cost on the sales order line, labeled as the *delivery product*."
msgstr ""
"I popup-fönstret *Lägg till en fraktmetod*, välj :guilabel:`Shiprocket` i "
"fältet :guilabel:`Fraktmetod`. Beräkna fraktpriset genom att klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Hämta anrop`. Klicka slutligen på :guilabel:`Lägg till` för "
"att inkludera fraktkostnaden på försäljningsorderraden, märkt som "
"*leveransprodukt*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Add Shiprocket shipping to a sales order."
msgstr "Lägg till Shiprocket-frakt till en försäljningsorder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:181
msgid ""
"Automatically calculate shipping costs for Shiprocket in both the **Sales** "
"and **eCommerce** applications."
msgstr ""
"Beräkna automatiskt transportkostnader för Shiprocket i både applikationerna "
"**Försäljning** och **Webbshop**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:184
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:212
msgid ""
"Then, :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery. Shipping label documents are "
"automatically generated in the chatter, which includes the following:"
msgstr ""
"Därefter :guilabel:`Validera` leveransen. Fraktsedeldokument genereras "
"automatiskt i chatten, som innehåller följande:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:187
msgid "**Shipping labels**, depending on the number of packages."
msgstr "**Transportetiketter**, beroende på antalet paket."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:188
msgid "**Tracking numbers**, if the selected courier supports it."
msgstr "**Spårningsnummer**, om den valda kurtjänsten stöder det."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "After the delivery is validated, a label is generated."
msgstr "När leveransen är validerad skapas en etikett."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:194
msgid ""
"If the shipment is too heavy for the configured Shiprocket service, the "
"weight is split to simulate multiple packages. Products must be put in "
"different packages to validate the transfer and generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Om leveransen är för tung för den konfigurerade Shiprocket-tjänsten delas "
"vikten upp för att simulera flera paket. Produkter måste placeras i olika "
"paket för att validera överföringen och skapa etiketter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:199
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:250
msgid "Cancellations"
msgstr "Avbokningar"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:201
msgid ""
"If a delivery order is canceled in Odoo, it is automatically archived in "
"Shiprocket. However, the cancellation will not be sent to the courier "
"directly, so make sure to log in to the courier's platform to handle it "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Om en leveransorder avbryts i Odoo arkiveras den automatiskt i Shiprocket. "
"Avbeställningen skickas dock inte direkt till kurirföretaget, så se till att "
"logga in på kurirföretagets plattform för att hantera det manuellt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:206
msgid "Turn on Shiprocket integration"
msgstr "Aktivera Shiprocket-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:208
msgid ""
"After the Shiprocket connection is set up, use the smart buttons at the top "
"of the form to publish, turn on production mode, or activate debug logging."
msgstr ""
"När Shiprocket-anslutningen är installerad använder du de smarta knapparna "
"överst i formuläret för att publicera, aktivera produktionsläge eller "
"aktivera felsökningsloggning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:211
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished/Published`: Click this smart button to make this "
"shipping method available on the **eCommerce** website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opublicerad/Publicerad`: Klicka på denna smarta knapp för att "
"göra denna leveransmetod tillgänglig på **Webbshop**-hemsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:213
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment/Production Environment`: Click this smart button "
"to specify whether labels are for testing only and are canceled immediately "
"(Test), or whether real shipping labels can be generated and charged to the "
"Shiprocket account (Production). In the Test environment, the amount of the "
"canceled shipment is refunded in 3 to 4 days."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Testmiljö/Produktionsmiljö`: Klicka på denna smarta knapp för att "
"ange om etiketter endast är för testning och avbryts omedelbart (Test), "
"eller om verkliga transportetiketter kan skapas och debiteras Shiprocket-"
"kontot (Produktion). I testmiljön återbetalas beloppet för den avbrutna "
"leveransen inom 3 till 4 dagar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:217
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug/Debug Requests`: Click this smart button to specify "
"whether API requests and responses are logged in Odoo (:doc:`turn on "
"developer mode <../../../../general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Logging`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ingen felsökning/Felsök förfrågningar`: Klicka på denna smarta "
"knapp för att ange om programmeringsgränssnitt-förfrågningar och svar loggas "
"i Odoo (:doc:`aktivera systemutvecklarläge <../../../../general/"
"developer_mode>` och gå till :menuselection:`Inställningar-appen --> Teknisk "
"--> Loggning`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:3
msgid "Starshipit shipping"
msgstr "Starshipit-frakt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Starshipit is a shipping service operator that facilitates the integration "
"of Australasian shipping couriers with Odoo. Once integrated, users can "
"create shipping methods that will automatically get rates from specific "
"couriers (such as Australia Post, NZ Post, DHL,...) based on predefined "
"conditions."
msgstr ""
"Starshipit är en frakttjänstoperatör som underlättar integrationen av "
"australiensiska fraktkurirer med Odoo. När det är integrerat kan användarna "
"skapa fraktmetoder som automatiskt får priser från specifika kurirer (t.ex. "
"Australia Post, NZ Post, DHL, ...) baserat på fördefinierade villkor."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:11
