#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:98
msgid "Forecasted date: Feb 19 (current date + vendor lead time)"
msgstr "Prognostiserat datum: 19 feb (aktuellt datum + leverantörens ledtid)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:100
msgid "**With horizon days (4 or more days)**"
msgstr "**Med horisontdagar (4 eller fler dagar)**"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:102
msgid "Odoo considers demand up to Feb 23 as relevant today (Feb 18)"
msgstr ""
"Odoo betraktar efterfrågan fram till den 23 feb som relevant idag (18 feb)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:103
msgid ""
"The need for 8 more units appears immediately in the replenishment report"
msgstr "Behovet av 8 enheter till visas omedelbart i påfyllningsrapporten"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:104
msgid ""
"Forecasted date: Feb 23 (current date + vendor lead time + horizon days)"
msgstr ""
"Prognostiserat datum: 23 feb (aktuellt datum + leverantörens ledtid + "
"horisontdagar)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:0
msgid "Show forecasted date brought forward."
msgstr "Visa framflyttat prognostiserat datum."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:110
msgid "Replenishment information"
msgstr "Påfyllningsinformation"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:112
msgid ""
"In each line of the replenishment report, clicking the :icon:`fa-info-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(info)` icon opens the :guilabel:`Replenishment "
"Information` pop-up window, which displays the *lead times* and *forecasted "
"date*."
msgstr ""
"På varje rad i påfyllningsrapporten öppnar ett klick på ikonen :icon:`fa-"
"info-circle` :guilabel:`(info)` popup-"
"fönstret :guilabel:`Påfyllningsinformation`, som visar *ledtider* och "
"*prognostiserat datum*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:116
msgid ""
"For detailed information on how to use this feature for replenishment, go to "
"the :doc:`just-in-time <just_in_time>` section."
msgstr ""
"För detaljerad information om hur du använder den här funktionen för "
"påfyllning, gå till avsnittet :doc:`just-in-time <just_in_time>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:120
msgid "Select a warehouse"
msgstr "Välj ett lager"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:122
msgid ""
"If a warehouse's replenishment method is :doc:`resupply from another "
"warehouse <resupply_warehouses>`, check for available product quantities in "
"other warehouses by opening the :guilabel:`Replenishment Information` pop-up "
"window. Warehouses that can replenish the stock are listed under "
"the :guilabel:`Warehouses` tab, and the :guilabel:`Available Quantity` shows "
"the on-hand stock in each warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Om ett lagers påfyllningsmetod är :doc:`påfyllning från ett annat lager "
"<resupply_warehouses>`, kontrollera tillgängliga produktkvantiteter i andra "
"lager genom att öppna popup-fönstret :guilabel:`Påfyllningsinformation`. "
"Lager som kan fylla på lagret listas under fliken :guilabel:`Lager`, "
"och :guilabel:`Tillgänglig kvantitet` visar lagersaldot i varje lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:128
msgid ""
"After selecting a sourcing warehouse, click :guilabel:`Select "
"Route` :guilabel:`Order` button is clicked, the reordering rule will revert "
"to its preferred route (Buy or Manufacture)."
msgstr ""
"Efter att ha valt ett anskaffningslager, klicka på :guilabel:`Välj "
"rutt` :guilabel:`Beställning`-knappen klickas, kommer ombeställningsregeln "
"att återgå till sin föredragna rutt (Köp eller Tillverka)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:None
msgid "The warehouse tab on the Replenishment Information pop-up window."
msgstr "Fliken \"Lager\" i popup-fönstret Påfyllningsinformation."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:135
msgid ":ref:`Temporary Reordering Rules <purchase/check-replenishment>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Tillfälliga ombeställningsregler <purchase/check-replenishment>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:3
msgid "Inter-warehouse replenishment"
msgstr "Påfyllning mellan lager"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:7
msgid ""
"When a business operates multiple locations, such as warehouses, retail "
"shops, or manufacturing facilities, resupplying stock from a central "
"warehouse is sometimes necessary. Odoo uses a *Route* configuration that "
"enables locations to replenish from a central distribution center, "
"automatically generating *inter-warehouse transfers*. "
"Odoo :guilabel:`Inventory` manages these transfers to keep stores in stock."
msgstr ""
"När ett företag driver flera platser, såsom lager, butiker eller "
"tillverkningsanläggningar, är det ibland nödvändigt att fylla på lager från "
"ett centralt lager. Odoo använder en konfiguration för *rutt* som gör det "
"möjligt för platser att fylla på från ett centralt distributionscenter, "
"vilket automatiskt genererar *överföringar mellan lager*. "
"Odoo :guilabel:`Lager` hanterar dessa överföringar för att hålla butikerna i "
"lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:13
msgid ""
"This guide explains how to conduct inter-warehouse transfers using two "
"replenishment strategies:"
msgstr ""
"Den här guiden förklarar hur man utför överföringar mellan lager med hjälp "
"av två påfyllningsstrategier:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:15
msgid ":ref:`Make to order (MTO) <inventory/warehouses_storage/MTO>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Beställningsstyrt (MTO) <inventory/warehouses_storage/MTO>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:16
msgid ":ref:`Reordering rule <inventory/warehouses_storage/reordering-rule>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ombeställningsregel <inventory/warehouses_storage/reordering-rule>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:19
msgid ":doc:`Difference between MTO and reordering rules <../replenishment>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Skillnad mellan MTO och ombeställningsregler <../replenishment>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:24
msgid ""
"The initial configuration for both replenishment strategies is the same. "
"First go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"In the :guilabel:`Warehouse` section, activate :guilabel:`Storage "
"Locations`. Then, click :guilabel:`Save` to apply the setting."
msgstr ""
"Den initiala konfigurationen är densamma för båda påfyllningsstrategierna. "
"Gå först till :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> Konfiguration --> "
"Inställningar`. I sektionen :guilabel:`Lager` aktiverar "
"du :guilabel:`Förvarplatser`. Klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Spara` för att "
"tillämpa inställningen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:None
msgid "Enable Storage Locations in Inventory settings."
msgstr "Aktivera Förvarplatser i Lagerinställningar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:35
msgid ""
"Configure the settings for the central warehouse and connecting storage "
"locations by going to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Warehouses`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurera inställningarna för det centrala lagret och anslutande "
"förvarplatser genom att gå till :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> "
"Konfiguration --> Lager`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:39
msgid ""
"Each central warehouse and other locations *must* have its own warehouse. "
"For example, each shop is considered a local warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Varje centralt lager och andra platser *måste* ha sitt eget lager. Till "
"exempel betraktas varje butik som ett lokalt lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:42
msgid ""
"Select an existing warehouse, or create a new one to be resupplied from the "
"central warehouse, by clicking :guilabel:`New`. Then, give the warehouse a "
"name and a :guilabel:`Short Name`, which will appear on that warehouse's "
"transfers."
msgstr ""
"Välj ett befintligt lager eller skapa ett nytt som ska fyllas på från det "
"centrala lagret genom att klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa`. Ge sedan lagret ett "
"namn och ett :guilabel:`Kortnamn`, som kommer att visas på lagrets "
"överföringar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:46
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Warehouse Configuration` tab, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Resupply From` field. Check the box next to the central "
"warehouse's name. If the warehouse can be resupplied by more than one "
"warehouse, make sure to check those warehouses' boxes too. Now, Odoo knows "
"which warehouses can resupply this warehouse."
msgstr ""
"På fliken :guilabel:`Lagerkonfiguration` letar du reda på "
"fältet :guilabel:`Fyll på från`. Kryssa för rutan bredvid det centrala "
"lagrets namn. Om lagret kan fyllas på från mer än ett lager, se till att "
"kryssa för dessa lagers rutor också. Nu vet Odoo vilka lager som kan fylla "
"på detta lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:52
msgid ""
"The central warehouse that will supply the shops is called `Central "
"warehouse`. The :guilabel:`Resupply From` field is set to this warehouse on "
"the shop's warehouse configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Det centrala lagret som ska förse butikerna kallas `Central warehouse`. "
"Fältet :guilabel:`Fyll på från` är inställt på detta lager på butikens "
"lagerkonfigurationssida."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:57
msgid ":doc:`../inventory_management/warehouses`"
msgstr ":doc:`../inventory_management/warehouses`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:None
msgid "Supply one warehouse with another in the Warehouse Configuration tab."
msgstr "Utrusta ett lager med ett annat på fliken Lagerkonfiguration."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:64
msgid "Set route on a product"
msgstr "Ange rutt för en produkt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:66
msgid ""
"Products must also be configured properly in order for them to be "
"transferred between warehouses."
msgstr ""
"Produkter måste också konfigureras korrekt för att de ska kunna överföras "
"mellan lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:68
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> Products` and select "
"the desired product."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> Produkter --> Produkter` och välj "
"önskad produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:70
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, the new route appears as :guilabel:`X: "
"Supply Product from Y` in the :guilabel:`Routes` section, where 'X' is the "
"store's warehouse that receives products, and 'Y' is the warehouse that "
"sends products."
msgstr ""
"På fliken :guilabel:`Lager` visas den nya rutten som :guilabel:`X: Supply "
"Product from Y` i sektionen :guilabel:`Rutter`, där \"X\" är butikens lager "
"som tar emot produkter och \"Y\" är lagret som skickar produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:74
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`X: Supply Product from Y` checkbox, which is intended to "
"be used with the |MTO| route or a reordering rule to replenish stock by "
"moving the product from one warehouse to another. Proceed to the dedicated "
"sections below to continue the process."
msgstr ""
"Kryssa för kryssrutan :guilabel:`X: Supply Product from Y`, som är avsedd "
"att användas med |MTO|-rutten eller en ombeställningsregel för att fylla på "
"lager genom att flytta produkten från ett lager till ett annat. Fortsätt "
"till de dedikerade avsnitten nedan för att fortsätta processen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:83
msgid ""
"To replenish products using the make-to-order method, go to the product form "
"and ensure the :ref:`MTO route is unarchived <inventory/mto/enable-mto>`, so "
"it appears in the :guilabel:`Routes` section of the :guilabel:`Inventory` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"För att fylla på produkter med make-to-order-metoden, gå till "
"produktformuläret och säkerställ att :ref:`MTO-rutten är avarkiverad "
"<inventory/mto/enable-mto>`, så att den visas i sektionen :guilabel:`Rutter` "
"på fliken :guilabel:`Lager`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:87
msgid ""
"With the resupply and |MTO| routes ticked, jump to the section "
"titled: :ref:`Replenish from another warehouse <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"resupply-workflow>`."
msgstr ""
"Med rutterna för återanskaffning och |MTO| ikryssade, hoppa till avsnittet "
"med titeln: :ref:`Fyll på från annat lager <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"resupply-workflow>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:91
