"`SHOP/Stock` och :guilabel:`Rutt` inställd på :guilabel:`Store: Resupply "
"from YourCompany`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:0
