#~ "select a subcontracted product in the :guilabel:`Product` drop-down menu, "
#~ "and enter a quantity in the :guilabel:`Quantity` field."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Välj kunden i rullgardinsmenyn :guilabel:`Customer`. Klicka sedan "
