#~ msgid ""
#~ "Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the |SO|, at which point "
#~ "a :guilabel:`Purchase` smart button appears at the top of the page. This "
#~ "opens the |PO| created to purchase the subcontracted product from the "
#~ "subcontractor."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Klicka på :guilabel:`Confirm` för att bekräfta |SO|, varvid "
