#~ "nytt :guilabel:`Blockerad av`-alternativ tillgängligt i inställningarna "
#~ "på fliken :guilabel:`Operationer`."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Next, click on the :guilabel:`Operations` tab. On the top-right of the "
#~ "tab, click on the tab's :guilabel:`settings` button, then enable "
#~ "the :guilabel:`Blocked By` checkbox. This makes a :guilabel:`Blocked By` "
